{"name":"军事后勤补给链模型","description":"后方仓库-运输线-前线三级补给链动态模型","engine":"SIMULATION_PACKAGE","simulation":{"algorithm":"RK4","time_start":0,"time_length":60,"time_step":0.5,"time_units":"DAYS"},"elements":[{"type":"STOCK","name":"Depot","behavior":{"initial_value":10000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[100,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"STOCK","name":"InTransit","behavior":{"initial_value":500,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[350,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"STOCK","name":"Frontline","behavior":{"initial_value":1000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[600,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"Production","behavior":{"value":"200"},"display":{"coordinates":[100,100],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"TransportCap","behavior":{"value":"150"},"display":{"coordinates":[300,100],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"ConsumeRate","behavior":{"value":"80"},"display":{"coordinates":[600,100],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"CombatLossRate","behavior":{"value":"0.02"},"display":{"coordinates":[720,380],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"DelayFactor","behavior":{"value":"0.05"},"display":{"coordinates":[350,420],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"Produce","from":null,"to":"Depot","behavior":{"value":"[Production]","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[100,180],"to_coordinates":[100,225]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"Dispatch","from":"Depot","to":"InTransit","behavior":{"value":"min([Depot], [TransportCap])","non_negative":true},"display":{}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"Deliver","from":"InTransit","to":"Frontline","behavior":{"value":"[InTransit] * [DelayFactor]","non_negative":true},"display":{}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"Consume","from":"Frontline","to":null,"behavior":{"value":"min([Frontline], [ConsumeRate])","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[660,275],"to_coordinates":[750,250]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"CombatLoss","from":"Frontline","to":null,"behavior":{"value"